WEBVTT

00:05:01.893 --> 00:05:07.070
Hivyo ukigundua mtoto wako wa miaka miwili
anakudanganya kwa mara ya kwanza,

00:05:07.094 --> 00:05:09.078
badala ya kushtushwa,

00:05:09.102 --> 00:05:10.594
unatakiwa usherehekee--

00:05:10.618 --> 00:05:12.140
(Kicheko)

00:05:12.164 --> 00:05:17.894
kwasababu inaashiria kwamba mtoto wako
amefikia hatua mpya

00:05:17.918 --> 00:05:19.553
ya ukuaji wa kawaida.

00:05:21.085 --> 00:05:24.221
Sasa, watoto hawadanganyi vizuri?

00:05:24.878 --> 00:05:27.872
Unafikiri unaweza kugundua
udanganyifu wao kirahisi?

00:05:28.745 --> 00:05:30.423
Ungependa kujaribu?